<p class="vi" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Nguồn: Seligman, M.E.P. &amp; Maier, S.F. (1967), "Failure to Escape Traumatic Shock," Journal of Experimental Psychology, 74(1), 1–9. Denrell, J. (2007), "Adaptive Learning and Risk Taking," Psychological Review, 114(1), 177–187. Seru, A., Shumway, T., &amp; Stoffman, N. (2010), "Learning by Trading," Review of Financial Studies, 23(2), 705–739. Thaler, R.H. &amp; Benartzi, S. (2004), "Save More Tomorrow: Using Behavioral Economics to Increase Employee Saving," Journal of Political Economy, 112(S1), S164–S187. Xác suất chuỗi thua lỗ do tác giả tự tính toán dựa trên phân phối nhị thức với giả định tỷ lệ thắng 55%.</p>
<p class="id" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sumber: Seligman, M.E.P. &amp; Maier, S.F. (1967), "Failure to Escape Traumatic Shock," Journal of Experimental Psychology, 74(1), 1–9. Denrell, J. (2007), "Adaptive Learning and Risk Taking," Psychological Review, 114(1), 177–187. Seru, A., Shumway, T., &amp; Stoffman, N. (2010), "Learning by Trading," Review of Financial Studies, 23(2), 705–739. Thaler, R.H. &amp; Benartzi, S. (2004), "Save More Tomorrow: Using Behavioral Economics to Increase Employee Saving," Journal of Political Economy, 112(S1), S164–S187. Probabilitas rentetan kekalahan dihitung sendiri oleh penulis berdasarkan distribusi binomial dengan asumsi tingkat kemenangan 55%.</p>
